content: Love it!!!

App is a little too pricey. I know you don't get any ads but your clean time date is so tiny and small it's difficult to see. There should be the ability to make the text bigger. Since the last Android update the program's notification system is not working properly. It's notifying me early early in the mornings as opposed to late in the morning when it's supposed to. I'm hoping there will be an update to fix that soon. Again price is a little too high for this program.

I have had this app for two years. It states your clean date clean time and the just for today. It does what it is supposed to every time. Seriously it's two pages once you put your clean date in you open it and it will swipe one page. Maybe they were high who knows
This is one of my best apps, I use this faithfully every morning! I don't know what I would do without it
